33,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:10:09.000Z","msg":"晒9氣<br />\n而家有公眾地方行為不檢俾你捉黑社會你都唔撚敢啦"},{"pid":"713191ec7db38a66203e4f838a615d38c1706575","tid":537633,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"狗警要屈大把方法,立法係門面嘢？"},{"pid":"e320193a02f16ae3078a68ea30d3a1013fafa24b","tid":537633,"uid":63350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"立到既話班警犬警畜會好撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}